===Adjective===
{{en-adj|wid|er}}

# Having a large physical extent from side to side.
#: ''We walked down a '''wide''' corridor.''
# Large in scope.
#: ''The inquiry had a '''wide''' remit.''
# {{context|sports|lang=en}} Operating at the side of the playing area.
#: ''That team needs a decent '''wide''' player.''
# {{context|tennis|lang=en}} (speaking of the ball) that bounces off the authorized court limits, referring to the horizontal dimension (and therefore is ''out''). 
#* ''Too bad! That what a great passing-shot, but it's '''wide'''. 

